This repository contains the various platform packaging bits. Each of the following subdirs contains the packaging for Chef, Ohai, and Mixlibs, and other packaged dependencies until said packages are stabilised in the respective platforms.

debian/ - debian and ubuntu
redhat/ - redhat, centos, fedora
gentoo/ - :)
openbsd/ - :)
freebsd/ - >:)

For contributing to the overall packaging, please see the Opscode wiki page on contributing:

  http://wiki.opscode.com/display/opscode/Contributing

And on working with our git repositories:

  http://wiki.opscode.com/display/opscode/Working+with+Git

Open tickets in Jira, CHEF project, be sure to use the "Packaging" component:

  http://tickets.opscode.com/

If you resolve a ticket, set the status to "Resolved" and assign Joshua Timberman.
